Class vc_ColorHistogramEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.vc_ColorHistogramEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<vc_ColorHistogramEntry>

    public class vc_ColorHistogramEntry
extends Object
implements Comparable<vc_ColorHistogramEntry>
    This class constitutes a single histogram entry, a coupling of color & frequency. Also implements a comparator to sort histogram entries based on frequency.
